data.description: Nestled in Bradley Point South, this spacious 4-bedroom home embodies comfort and elegance. Upon entry, you'll be greeted by a large living area that effortlessly flows into the rest of the home. The kitchen features stunning granite countertops, new flooring, stainless appliances, and a cozy breakfast nook overlooking the backyard. Just up the stairs is a spacious loft, full of possibilities as an extra living space. The luxurious primary suite features vaulted ceilings, a spa-inspired en suite bath, and two large closets. Three additional bedrooms and a full bath complete the second floor. Step outside to a private oasis - a tranquil backyard with a patio and wooden fence for privacy. The 2-car garage boasts convenient shelving for added storage. Enjoy access to neighborhood amenities including the clubhouse, pool with a splash area, fitness facilities, playground, and tennis courts. Offered as-is, this home has been thoughtfully updated with fresh paint and new carpet.
